<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    
    <!-- CSP bloqueia scripts externos não autorizados -->
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Security-Policy" 
          content="default-src 'self'; 
                   script-src 'self'; 
                   style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; 
                   img-src 'self' data: https:;
                   font-src 'self';
                   connect-src 'self';
                   frame-ancestors 'none';
                   base-uri 'self';
                   form-action 'self';">
    
    <!-- Proteções adicionais -->
    <meta http-equiv="X-Content-Type-Options" content="nosniff">
    <meta http-equiv="X-Frame-Options" content="DENY">
    <meta name="referrer" content="strict-origin-when-cross-origin">
    
    <title>Site Seguro</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background: #0a0a0f;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        
        .security-badge {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00b894 0%, #00cec9 100%);
            color: #0a0a0f;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .container {
            background: #16161d;
            border: 1px solid #2d2d3a;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 3rem;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.75rem;
        }
        
        p {
            color: #a0a0a0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .feature-list {
            text-align: left;
            list-style: none;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
        }
        
        .feature-list li {
            padding: 0.75rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #2d2d3a;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }
        
        .feature-list li::before {
            content: "✓";
            color: #00b894;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .feature-list li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
            background: #00b894;
            color: #0a0a0f;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            background: #00cec9;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
<base target="_blank">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="security-badge">
        🔒 Conexão Segura • Dados Protegidos
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Bem-vindo ao Site Seguro</h1>
        <p>Este site implementa múltiplas camadas de proteção para garantir sua privacidade.</p>
        
        <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>CSP (Content Security Policy) ativo</li>
            <li>Proteção contra clickjacking</li>
            <li>Headers de segurança configurados</li>
            <li>Sem rastreamento de terceiros</li>
            <li>Conexão HTTPS obrigatória</li>
        </ul>
        
        <a href="#saiba-mais" class="btn">Saiba Mais</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
